          ],
          "returns": "Self"
        }
      ],
      "docs": "Interactor implementing CatalogueImplSignalsService. Orchestrates per-layer A/B/C TypeGraph fetch, signal evaluator invocation, and region-by-region result formatting. Injected dependencies: CatalogueDocumentLoaderPort (A-side catalogue file load), CatalogueToExtendedCratePort (A-side CatalogueDocument → ExtendedCrate conversion), SignalEvaluatorPort (Phase 1 + Phase 2 evaluation), RustdocCratePort (B-side baseline load via load_from_path; C-side live capture via capture_current), TdddLayerBindingsPort (architecture-rules.json enumeration). apps/cli constructs the concrete infrastructure adapters (FsCatalogueDocumentLoader, CatalogueToExtendedCrateCodec, SignalEvaluatorV2, RustdocCrateAdapter, FsTdddLayerBindingsAdapter) and injects them at the composition root. [source: ADR 2026-05-11-2330 D2]",
      "spec_refs": [
        { "file": "track/items/tddd-v2-2026-05-08/spec.json", "anchor": "IN-18", "hash": "25956e359d8c1c93d9ce4901902f3ae0108b25bcf0cda2597b20addad58a704a" },
        { "file": "track/items/tddd-v2-2026-05-08/spec.json", "anchor": "IN-17", "hash": "f3302fe868e8c61ed23817d97159e9696aa2224a3942e534a4d5e94f62851127" }
      ],
      "informal_grounds": []
    },
