      ],
      "docs": "Error variants for RenderContractMap::execute. Modified: removed stale UnknownKindFilter variant (baseline was captured before T003 removed it); corrected variant payloads to match actual enum (tuple and struct variants, not unit). thiserror #[from] generates From<CatalogueLoaderError> and From<ContractMapWriterError>; declared with explicit generic_args to disambiguate the two impls. Also Display/Error for thiserror-generated impls.",
